# Parameter correlations

This directory contains the details of correlations between fit parameters
for the data sets in the NANOGrav 15-year data release.

For each yaml, `configs/J1234+5678.nb.yaml`, this script creates three files:

* `J1234+5678.nb.correlation.txt` that is a human-readable list 
  of large pairwise correlations
* `J1234+5678.nb.correlation.npz` that is a machine-readable file 
  containing the whole correlation file and some additional data
* `J1234+5678.nb.correlation.hdf5` that is an HDF5 file 
  containing the whole correlation file and some additional data

